      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nThis passed the sanityn test and handled both error conditions:\n\nhttps://testing.hpdd.intel.com/sub_tests/ec138e0a-5206-11e5-9a74-5254006e85c2\n\n CMD: onyx-38vm4 lctl set_param ost.OSS.ost_io.nrs_policies=orr\n CMD: onyx-38vm4 lctl set_param ost.OSS.*.nrs_orr_quantum=1\nonyx-38vm4: error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/ost/OSS/ost_io/nrs_orr_quantum=1: No such device\nost.OSS.ost_io.nrs_orr_quantum=1\n CMD: onyx-38vm4 lctl set_param ost.OSS.ost_io.nrs_policies=orr\n CMD: onyx-38vm4 lctl set_param ost.OSS.*.nrs_orr_quantum=1\nonyx-38vm4: error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/ost/OSS/ost_io/nrs_orr_quantum=1: Resource temporarily unavailable",
